vote.title: An ordinance amending Chapter 43, "Streets and Sidewalks," of the Dallas City Code by amending Article X. “Dockless Vehicle Permit” to (1) provide definitions; (2) designate authority; (3) provide permitting guidelines and requirements; (4) provide a saving clause; (5) provide a severability clause; and (6) provide an effective date - Estimated Revenue: General Fund $200,000.00 (see Fiscal Information)
